com.gotenna.sdk.data.user

Class UserDataStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gotenna.sdk.data.user.UserDataStore

  • public final class UserDataStore
extends java.lang.Object
    A singleton that keeps track of the current user identified with the goTenna.

      • addGroupGID

        public void addGroupGID(long groupGID)
        Adds the group GID to the list of the current user's valid group GIDs.

        This method is called automatically via GTCommandCenter.createGroupWithGIDs(List, GTCommandCenter.GTGroupInviteResponseListener, GTCommandCenter.GTGroupInviteErrorListener)

        It is also automatically called when an incoming GTGroupCreationMessageData is detected.

        Parameters:
        groupGID - The group GID to add.

      • hasGroupGID

        public boolean hasGroupGID(long groupGID)

        Parameters:
        groupGID - The group GID to check.
        Returns:
        True if this group GID already exists in the current user's cached info, false otherwise.

      • addMulticastGroupGID

        public void addMulticastGroupGID(long groupGID)
        Adds the multicast group GID to the list of the user's valid group GIDs.

        This method is called automatically via GTCommandCenter.createMulticastGroup(long)

        Only pre-approve SDK users can leverage this functionality.

        Parameters:
        groupGID - The group GID to add.

      • hasMulticastGroupGID
